Maureen Pryor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maureen_Pryor 0 Maureen Pryor (23 May 1922 – 5 May 1977) was an Irish-born English character actress who made stage, film, and television appearances. The Encyclopaedia of British Film noted, "she never played leads, but, with long rep and TV experience (from 1949), she was noticeable in all she did."
